285
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,340
Why the long face?

286
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,580
Is it about the medical disputes?

287
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,700
We've seen this kind of thing many times.

288
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,940
That guy with the little mustache is a pro at medical disputes.

289
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,770
You see him outside every hospital.

290
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:31,010
No matter what,

291
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:32,940
it's still a hassle for the hospital.

292
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,700
I'll take responsibility for this.

293
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:38,700
This way, you'll have an explanation.

294
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,650
Mr. Qin isn't here,

295
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:42,130
but it's the same if I tell you.

296
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,460
No.

297
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,060
Mr. Du,

298
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:46,820
