299
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,010
Gemu is a big ship.

300
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:49,700
How could it sail without you as the captain?

301
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,580
Besides, if you leave,

302
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,650
wouldn't that mean Gemu is responsible for ruining someone's face?

303
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,770
I can't agree with that.

304
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,700
It's not just my problem.

305
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,770
I've advised them,

306
00:14:01,790 --> 00:14:02,700
but they wouldn't listen.

307
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,820
They said they've been with me for so many years.

308
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,340
Gemu still has you at the helm.

309
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,530
Handling light cosmetic procedures will be a breeze.

310
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,460
It's about money, right?

311
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:18,060
Not long ago, plastic surgery indeed had some difficulties.

312
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,460
But I've already discussed it with Mr. Qin,

313
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,730
and I've requested a subsidy.

314
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:21,770
It's going through finance.

315
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:23,180
It'll be distributed this afternoon.

316
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,340
These five years,

317
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:28,100
you and Mr. Qin have really been amazing to me.

318
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:31,010
Now we have the level 4 license.

319
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,580
The hospital is on track.

320
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,940
I guess I can finally retire.

321
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,010
After all, I'm a doctor.

322
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,610
I'm into the profession.

323
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,340
You know the dinosaur girl, right?

324
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,060
She came to me first.

325
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,300
I was thinking of doing it,

326
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:46,980
but does our hospital have the capability?

327
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:50,650
Now, she's gone to the Third Hospital.

328
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,650
I came from the Third Hospital.

329
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,650
When you all came to find me,

330
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:57,530
we agreed to build up Gemu

331
00:14:57,550 --> 00:14:58,300
together.

332
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,770
But now,

333
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:01,220
we can't even do

334
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,370
any challenging surgeries.

335
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,340
All we do is double eyelids.

336
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,890
And we're being criticized for turning plastic surgery into disfigurement.

337
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,460
What am I even doing here?

338
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,220
Mr. Du resigned.

339
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,100
Dr. Liang and the others

340
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,420
left too.

341
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,820
Our plastic surgery department

342
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:24,010
had two stars, Mr. Du and Ms. Zhou.

343
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,060
But now,

344
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:27,250
only Ms. Zhou remains.

345
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,850
Even if her skills are great, she can't carry it all alone.

346
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:33,340
It's been rumored that plastic surgery will merge with dermatology

347
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,610
and transform into light cosmetic procedures.

348
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:35,610
With all this fuss,

349
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,300
it might really happen.

350
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,850
Isn't Ms. Zhou the founder of the hospital?

351
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:42,250
Even if plastic surgery merges with dermatology,

352
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:43,730
it won't affect her.

353
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:46,940
You're new here,

354
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,770
so you might not understand.

355
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,850
Let me explain.

356
00:15:50,390 --> 00:15:53,340
Our plastic surgery department is like a latte.

357
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,820
Dermatology is like an Americano.

358
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,300
The latte is the hospital's signature.

359
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,530
We built our reputation on it.

360
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,940
But now,

361
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:03,700
the sales of Americano are several times that of the latte.

362
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:05,850
So Li's idea is

363
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:08,060
that we stop selling lattes.

364
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:09,130
If customers want it,

365
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,340
they can order Americano with milk.

366
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,580
It tastes the same, but costs less.

367
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,180
But they're different.

368
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,370
You've hit the point.

369
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:17,890
So once the merge happens,

370
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:21,980
the latte will be completely phased out.

371
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,980
I don't want latte.

372
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:26,180
Let's switch.

373
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:27,700
I had that already!

374
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:55,890
