378
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,820
Reassemble the shattered bones.

379
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:03,820
Fix them with titanium mesh.

380
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,490
Just imagine this like a jigsaw puzzle.

381
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:08,900
We need to put the smashed cheekbones

382
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,810
