383
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,460
It needs to be assembled properly.

384
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,860
This young man has such a good appearance.

385
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:14,490
Right?

386
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:15,770
Titanium mesh.

387
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:22,490
Now is the time to test your artistic skills.

388
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,420
Plastic surgery isn't just a technical job.

389
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,330
It also requires artistic sense.

390
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,810
My hands are so sore.

391
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:36,620
Five whole hours.

392
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,860
How is Dr. Qiao not tired?

393
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,290
Let me tell you,

394
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,330
five surgeries in a day,

395
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,980
she might be a bit tired.

396
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,530
Ten surgeries,

397
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,050
she gets more and more energetic.

398
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,980
If it's twenty surgeries,

399
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,330
she wouldn't even need to sleep.

400
00:17:50,350 --> 00:17:51,180
When someone's face is shattered,

401
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,660
she's like she's on a high from adrenaline.

402
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:54,090
To quote her famous saying,

403
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,380
"If you're tired from surgeries,

404
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,570
why even do it?"

405
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:59,900
From now on, any surgeries like this from emergency,

406
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,330
send them directly to me.

407
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,290
You're pretty good at imitating.

408
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:04,330
Why don't you become an actor?

409
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:07,140
Thanks.

410
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,050
Dr. Qiao, lunch is ready.

411
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:13,980
