412
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,530
Still the same old stuff?

413
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,980
Who ordered takeout?

414
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:18,770
I did.

415
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,770
Could you be a bit more creative?

416
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:24,090
Your brain is for thinking.

417
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:26,050
Your eyes are for discovering beauty.

418
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:29,530
You didn't even put any thought into the takeout.

419
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,460
How can you innovate in your skills?

420
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:38,380
Just finished surgery, looking for something to eat.

421
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:40,380
What's new?

422
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:03,050
My cookies!

423
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:04,380
Fang Ting,

424
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:06,330
female, 23 years old.

425
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,290
Fibrous dysplasia of bone.

426
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:09,770
She started showing symptoms at 12.

427
00:19:09,790 --> 00:19:11,900
By now, she has developed a tumor

428
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:14,620
as large as her skull and brain.

429
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:17,220
The Department of Plastic Surgery at our hospital has been around for decades,

430
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,940
and this is the first time we've encountered one this big.

431
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,490
Actually, this case

432
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,700
has already spread throughout the industry.

433
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:25,290
More than thirty specialized hospitals nationwide

434
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:26,330
dared not take it in.

435
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,050
Until last week,

436
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,380
they finally found us.

437
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,660
The blood supply to the tumor is extremely rich,

438
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,490
involving the entire face.

439
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,250
If bleeding occurs during the surgery,

440
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,700
it may be impossible to finish the operation.

441
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,460
No one can guarantee a hundred percent success.

442
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:40,380
This surgery is indeed difficult,

443
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,420
but based on our hospital's capabilities,

444
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,770
there shouldn't be any problems.

445
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:46,330
Since the patient is already here,

446
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:48,810
we shouldn't turn her away.

447
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:51,660
I've already met with the patient's family.

448
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:54,490
I told them they should've come to the Third Hospital earlier.

449
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:56,700
Ji,

450
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,380
please present the surgical plan

451
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,570
to everyone.

452
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,570
Our approach is as follows:

453
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:09,290
On the premise of minimizing risks,

454
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,900
we will first solve the issues of visibility

455
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,810
and ventilation.

456
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:12,730
We want the patient's life

457
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,860
to be completely self-sufficient.

458
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,900
The tumor occupies two-thirds of the face

459
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,140
and one-third of the skull.

460
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:18,290
Our surgery

461
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,940
will only remove the portion above the nostrils,

462
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,250
keeping everything below the nostrils intact.

463
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:22,490
The excised part

464
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:24,380
makes up about 20% of the overall distortion.

465
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,490
It's not a large proportion.

466
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,250
Just 20%.

467
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:31,730
I'm already looking forward to this surgery.

468
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:33,010
This will be

469
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:34,860
another classic battle for our hospital.

470
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:35,570
Excuse me.

471
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:37,490
There are still some shortcomings in the surgical plan.

472
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:40,010
Is there any other input from the team?

473
00:20:47,790 --> 00:20:48,860
The neurosurgery team has no objections.

474
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,770
We have no objections either.

475
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:51,700
No objections.

476
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,420
We have no objections.

477
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,290
We'll fully cooperate.

478
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:55,180
Alright.

479
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:57,090
I believe this surgery

480
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:58,940
will showcase our Third Hospital's level

481
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,730
to both the nation and internationally.

482
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:03,090
I hope all departments will work closely together.

483
00:21:03,350 --> 00:21:04,530
Let's all give it our best effort.

484
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:06,460
Since no one has any objections,

485
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:08,570
let's call it a day.

486
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,290
Alright.

487
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:10,290
Meeting adjourned.

488
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,490
I have an objection.

489
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,570
