490
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,090
You weren't here.

491
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,010
What objection do you have?

492
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,220
I just want to ask,

493
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,050
isn't it still our duty as doctors

494
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:22,090
to treat and save lives?

495
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:22,770
Thanks.

496
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:24,460
Don't put labels on us.

497
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,860
