498
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,090
We all have things to do.

499
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:29,330
What I mean is,

500
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,220
for other hospitals,

501
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:34,180
20% resection is indeed difficult.

502
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,860
But for our hospital,

503
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:36,860
it's a sure thing.

504
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,290
There's absolutely no problem.

505
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:39,700
