506
00:21:39,790 --> 00:21:41,570
A 20% partial resection

507
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:43,570
is not the patient's real need.

508
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:45,180
If we're going to cut, it should be total resection.

509
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,570
I've already looked at a lot of materials.

510
00:21:51,590 --> 00:21:53,010
The plan is ready.

511
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:55,330
I just need a little more time to refine it,

512
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,700
and I guarantee I can come up with

513
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:58,530
a plan that will satisfy both the hospital leadership and the patient.

