528
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:38,220
The chief surgeon is

529
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:41,660
our most skilled Dr. Ji.

530
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,660
We will first

531
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:48,050
solve the issues of visibility and ventilation,

