Fell down?

566
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,420
Let me see.

567
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,010
- Can you move your wrist? - It hurt!

568
00:24:37,030 --> 00:24:38,250
Where does it hurt? Here?

569
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,330
Ah!

570
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,220
This looks like a fibula fracture.

571
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:42,900
I've already confirmed it.

572
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,460
Where can I find a splint this late?

573
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:47,570
Xu,

574
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:49,220
get the first aid kit from my car.

575
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,620
Can you move your hand?

576
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:51,570
Yes.

577
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,010
Dong, call 120.

578
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:53,460
Okay.

579
00:24:53,550 --> 00:24:54,770
You didn't hit the back of your head, right?

580
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,380
Hello, is this 120?

581
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,490
No.

582
00:24:57,790 --> 00:24:59,490
Yes, one of my teammates is injured.

583
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:01,660
We're near Dacheng North Road.

584
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:05,770
Hang in there.

585
00:25:05,790 --> 00:25:07,050
Let me just stabilize it for now.

586
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:11,490
You're also a doctor?

587
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:12,730
A surgeon?

588
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:13,980
What about you?

589
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:16,420
Can't you tell?

590
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,490
So, with this situation,

591
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:22,860
do we have a choice between full resection and 20% resection?

592
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:26,330
Yes, full resection is riskier,

593
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:27,620
but 20% resection is less risky.

594
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,810
Doesn't mean there's no risk.

595
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,250
And for the hospital,

596
00:25:30,270 --> 00:25:31,860
doing such a high-difficulty surgery

597
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:33,250
is a good way to promote itself.

598
00:25:33,270 --> 00:25:35,140
The doctors can write papers to earn promotions.

599
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,050
And for the patient,

600
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:37,220
she used to have a giant tumor,

601
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:38,980
and after surgery, she just ended up with a big lump.

602
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,050
She still can't go out.

603
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:41,900
She still can't live normally.

604
00:25:42,550 --> 00:25:43,860
So, what's the point of this surgery?

605
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:45,420
Why should a patient risk their life

606
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,530
to undergo such a surgery?

607
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:47,980
What's the point?

608
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:48,860
Hold on a second.

609
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:49,620
Let me ask you something.

610
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,730
What's the point of you joining this cycling team?

611
00:25:52,590 --> 00:25:53,250
What's up?

612
00:25:53,510 --> 00:25:54,250
Look around.

613
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,660
Everyone here has had a long, tiring day.

614
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:57,940
Is anyone talking about work?

615
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,010
I'm not tired.

616
00:25:59,030 --> 00:25:59,940
Just relax, okay?

617
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:02,380
Can we leave work in the operating room?

618
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,700
I'm talking to you about this

619
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,050
because you're also a doctor.

620
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,810
This world is competitive enough as it is.

621
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:09,330
Good thing you're not my colleague.

622
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,490
If I ever get the chance to work with you,

623
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:12,660
I'd make sure to outdo you first.

624
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,700
The surgery failed.

625
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,980
Why don't you have some water?

626
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,180
Have some water, okay?

627
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,140
Calm down.

628
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:20,090
Calm down.

629
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,810
Can you let me say a few words?

630
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:24,250
I'm Zhou Jingwen, a partner at Geme Medical.

631
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:25,700
I'm also the head of plastic surgery.

632
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:27,620
Regarding the rumors about Du Jun's resignation...

633
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,460
I don't know why it got spread like this.

634
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:31,330
But the truth is, yesterday morning,

635
00:26:31,350 --> 00:26:33,250
he was dismissed by our board of directors.

636
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:34,250
Dismissed? He's such a well-regarded director.

637
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,220
Why was he dismissed?

638
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,330
There must be a problem.

639
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:39,180
Whether in medical skills or ethics,

640
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,620
Du Jun has proven to be a very disappointing doctor.

641
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:44,490
If any of Du Jun's patients are here,

642
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:45,620
I will take over all of them.

643
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,090
Who are you?

644
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,860
Everyone, please calm down.

645
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,380
Let's hear what our director has to say, okay?

646
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:50,900
It's fine.

647
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,090
If you're not familiar with me,

648
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:53,530
you can check the doctor profile wall in the lobby

649
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:54,620
to see my credentials.

650
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:56,090
Or search my name online

651
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:58,220
and you'll find my previous surgical cases.

652
00:26:58,350 --> 00:26:58,980
Yeah, you can look it up.

653
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,940
Stop bluffing.

654
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:01,010
Your surgeries are fully booked.

655
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:01,900
Where would you find the time?

656
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,660
Can I still have my surgery next Monday?

657
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,700
Understood. I'll do my best.

658
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:07,220
Next, my assistant will handle

659
00:27:07,240 --> 00:27:08,460
the scheduling for you.

660
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,980
There's another good piece of news.

661
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:12,090
The doctor replacing Du Jun will be here soon.

662
00:27:12,110 --> 00:27:14,140
He's the best doctor in our field.

663
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:14,980
You can rest assured.

664
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,940
You have to trust our hospital, really.

665
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,290
We'll arrange the best doctors for everyone.

666
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:20,140
Where are you?

667
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,700
There's a bit of a situation here.

668
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:22,700
It's best if you come over right away.

669
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:23,620
Check it online.

670
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,090
Zhou Jingwen,

671
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,140
you don't deserve to be a doctor.

672
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:53,290
Qiao Yang,

673
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,220
we'll see about that.

674
00:28:09,750 --> 00:28:11,620
I heard the surgery is very risky.

675
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,010
Are you scared?

676
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:17,730
No matter how you look at it, I'm winning.

677
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,490
If it fails,

678
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,090
it's just a chance to reincarnate.

679
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,180
Maybe I'll be a pretty girl in my next life.

680
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:27,660
Dear,

681
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,530
who did the surgery on that "dinosaur girl"?

682
00:28:39,310 --> 00:28:40,530
Mr. Li, what's wrong?

683
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:43,090
Mr. Qin just left a few days ago.

684
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:44,250
And now something this big happens?

685
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:46,140
Why isn't Du even answering my calls?

686
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,490
What's going on?

687
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:50,620
Enough. What's your situation?

688
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:53,140
Low pressure 120, high pressure 160.

689
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,420
And you're still getting worked up?

690
00:28:55,510 --> 00:28:57,010
If Du isn't answering his phone,

691
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:59,490
it means he's captaining another ship.

692
00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:02,010
No point wasting words with you.

693
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,490
Did you take your medication today?

694
00:29:03,510 --> 00:29:04,220
I'm taking it now.

695
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:05,730
Mr. Tang,

696
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:07,290
I'm really sorry.

697
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,530
There were so many guests this morning.

698
00:29:09,550 --> 00:29:12,140
I was so busy I didn't even drink water or eat.

699
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,490
Have you eaten?

700
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,380
Wanna order something together?

701
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:14,860
No need.

702
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,940
I have high blood pressure, I'm taking medication.

703
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,420
I don't need anything either, my stomach hurts.

704
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:23,090
When I left yesterday,

705
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:24,570
you should have left with me.

706
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:25,530
Yeah.

707
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,900
Ms. Li, you're pushing yourself too hard.

708
00:29:28,270 --> 00:29:30,090
From now on, leave these social engagements to Qin Gui.

709
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,700
Can I really avoid drinking?

710
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:35,140
Our industry is so fiercely competitive.

711
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:36,900
The equipment you want

712
00:29:37,110 --> 00:29:38,620
updates every year.

713
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:41,090
Why does Geme Medical always get the first batch?

714
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:43,250
Isn't it all thanks to me drinking bottle after bottle for it?

715
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:45,490
If Geme Medical wants to do well,

716
00:29:45,830 --> 00:29:46,900
Tang provides the money.

717
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:50,180
Jingwen has medical skills and knows management.

718
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,420
I don't have any other skills.

719
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:54,490
I can only sacrifice my liver

720
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,660
and give up my stomach.

721
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,940
Huai Shan Beef Tripe Soup.

722
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:01,140
Good for the liver and stomach, order this one.

723
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:04,940
You still have the mindset to eat something so delicate?

724
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,810
Tell me, what's going on with the plastic surgery department?

725
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:07,980
The profits aren't going up,

726
00:30:08,270 --> 00:30:09,730
but the problems never stop.

727
00:30:09,750 --> 00:30:11,900
At the beginning of the year, I invested millions

728
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,220
to buy you new equipment.

729
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:15,700
And yet, that cosmetic surgery failure

730
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,220
hasn't blown over, has it?

731
00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:18,490
The director ran off,

732
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,050
taking three attending surgeons with him.

733
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:21,570
And those three were our most profitable ones!

734
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:22,900
Isn't that just adding fuel to the fire?

735
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:25,220
Now the reputation of our Gemu Hospital

736
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,290
is about to be ruined by your plastic surgery department.

737
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:29,250
Tell me, how do you plan to solve this?

738
00:30:30,030 --> 00:30:31,700
Merge the plastic surgery and dermatology departments,

739
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:33,530
transition to minimally invasive cosmetic procedures,

740
00:30:34,270 --> 00:30:35,380
that would solve everything, wouldn't it?

741
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,380
Mr. Tang,

742
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:40,620
isn't that your idea?

743
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,250
Of course it is.

744
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:44,460
And didn't Ms. Li always say

745
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,180
it's the trend of the industry?

746
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,620
Ms. Zhou,

747
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,940
you can't just

748
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,620
keep burying your heads in the operating room.

749
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,420
Take some time to go out

750
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:55,660
and see how the industry is developing.

751
00:30:56,030 --> 00:30:56,700
Mr. Tang,

752
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,980
you just came from Hanzhong Street, right?

753
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:01,090
Have you counted

754
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:02,860
how many minimally invasive cosmetic clinics are on that street?

755
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,140
Four.

756
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:07,250
One street has four clinics.

757
00:31:07,270 --> 00:31:09,460
Now think about how many streets we have in Rongchuan.

758
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:10,460
Minimally invasive cosmetic clinics

759
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,980
are more common than nail salons.

760
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,140
I spent money to buy equipment

761
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:15,860
and fought hard to get the Level 4 surgery license,

762
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:17,660
all to set us apart from them.

763
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,810
What they can't do,

764
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,050
Gemu can.

765
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:22,620
That's the core competitive advantage of Gemu.

766
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,490
Ms. Li, isn't that right?

767
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,660
Of course.

768
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,700
Tang, you're just too anxious.

769
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,810
Who else would have high blood pressure if not you?

770
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:33,860
We've already said that merging the departments is a strategic direction,

771
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,010
it needs long-term planning.

772
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:38,700
Right now, there are more urgent issues to address.

773
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:40,660
Ms. Zhou,

774
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,570
Mr. Tang, look.

775
00:31:42,270 --> 00:31:44,010
This is the latest case from the Third Hospital.

776
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:46,010
It's the nationally followed Dinosaur Girl case.

777
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:48,620
The chief surgeon was their youngest department director,

778
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,490
Ji Xuefeng.

779
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,660
Do you know this person?

780
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:55,050
You're thinking of having him replace Du Jun?

781
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:56,250
Is that reliable?

782
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,180
His skills are excellent.

783
00:31:58,510 --> 00:32:00,250
And he just took on Fang Ting's surgery.

784
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:02,860
Right now, he's a key talent being cultivated at the Third Hospital.

785
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,570
He's expected to become the director in the future.

786
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:08,180
Imagine the future director of the Third Hospital

787
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,770
coming to Gemu to be our director...

788
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:13,380
Wouldn't that instantly resolve our trust crisis?

789
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,290
Wait.

790
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:16,180
I didn't get most of that,

791
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:17,860
but one thing I did understand.

792
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:20,490
He's the prospective director of the Third Hospital,

793
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:21,140
right?

794
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:24,220
Then why would he leave to come to Gemu?

795
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,460
Be a bit more realistic.

796
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,620
Can you just talk properly?

797
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:28,730
You're being too much.

798
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:31,940
Ms. Zhou has worked so hard for Gemu.

799
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,810
Let's set a deadline.

800
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:38,090
Within one month,

801
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,010
if you can really

802
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,420
recruit Ji Xuefeng to Gemu,

803
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,810
then it'll be an acceptable answer to Mr. Tang.

804
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:47,620
Fine, you have the final say.

805
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,570
But what if you can't recruit him?

806
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:51,250
Then the dermatology and plastic surgery departments will be merged.

807
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,220
As for my position,

808
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,090
you can decide as you please.

809
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:08,730
I'm back.

810
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,700
Weren't you supposed to come back tomorrow?

811
00:33:13,070 --> 00:33:14,660
When my wife summons me,

812
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:17,980
how could I not book the earliest flight?

813
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,700
I rushed back without stopping.

814
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,140
Alright.

815
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:23,700
Still working so late?

816
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:25,980
Haven't washed your hands, go wash them.

817
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,570
Didn't we already handle

818
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:34,620
most of Du Jun's surgery issue?

819
00:33:35,270 --> 00:33:36,730
Why did it blow up again?

820
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:39,460
I guess he has long planned to resign.

821
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:40,730
He just found a convenient excuse to do so.

822
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,980
As for why the public outcry got so big...

823
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:48,090
Someone's clearly targeting us from behind the scenes.

824
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,810
I'm not sure who it is yet.

825
00:33:50,110 --> 00:33:51,290
Is there any food at home?

826
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,090
I'm hungry.

827
00:33:52,510 --> 00:33:53,770
Didn't you eat on the plane?

828
00:33:53,790 --> 00:33:54,570
I fell asleep.

829
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:56,900
I'll make you some instant noodles.

830
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:00,700
From what Mr. Tang was saying,

831
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:03,620
if the plastic surgery and dermatology departments don't merge,

832
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:06,770
we can't resolve the cosmetic surgery failure issue.

833
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:08,740
It sounds like if we don't do it,

834
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:10,090
Gemu will be done for.

835
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,380
But I've been thinking about it,

836
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:15,130
it doesn't make sense.

837
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,210
Anyway, Tang Jun

838
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:18,570
just listens to Li Qi.

839
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,380
He keeps talking about minimally invasive cosmetic procedures

840
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,780
have low cost and quick returns.

841
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:25,130
Now, whatever projects we plan,

842
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:27,340
they all have to get past Li Qi first.

843
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,260
You know, those two

844
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,340
are so cringy.

845
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:34,380
I swear,

846
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:36,610
Li Qi practically wanted to shove that medicine right into Tang's mouth.

847
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:39,460
It gave me goosebumps all over.

848
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,460
To be fair,

849
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,340
Mr. Tang does have a bit of a temper,

850
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:46,210
but he's not a bad guy.

851
00:34:47,230 --> 00:34:49,490
Back when no one believed in us,

852
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:52,650
he was the only one who firmly invested in Gemu.

853
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:53,490
Come on, give me a break.

854
00:34:53,510 --> 00:34:55,490
He only cares about immediate gains,

855
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:57,570
never thinks beyond three steps ahead.

856
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,300
He's just lucky,

857
00:34:59,630 --> 00:35:00,530
coming from money.

858
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,260
With his brains,

859
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:04,210
he should have gone bankrupt eight hundred times by now.

860
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:11,090
Have you thought about

861
00:35:12,030 --> 00:35:13,300
how to approach Ji Xuefeng?

862
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,980
No idea. I'll figure it out when I get there.

863
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:20,260
When Mr. Du left the Third Hospital,

864
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,210
it was all over the place.

865
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:24,170
Now you're going to look for him,

866
00:35:24,190 --> 00:35:25,460
but without any connections,

867
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,820
I'm worried

868
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,050
you won't even get in the door.

869
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,090
What else can I do?

870
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:32,090
We're stuck at this point already.

871
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:33,650
I don't know.

872
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:34,820
Just thinking about it gives me a headache.

873
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:35,980
Alright.

874
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,260
Don't stress.

875
00:35:38,590 --> 00:35:40,340
As my dad always says,

876
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,260
as long as your mindset doesn't slip,

877
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:44,460
there are always more solutions than problems.

878
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,570
You know what?

879
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,570
It was crazy this time when I went back.

880
00:35:48,590 --> 00:35:50,610
At that dinner table, besides me,

881
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:53,050
everyone else has at least two kids.

882
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:55,130
Remember my cousin?

883
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:57,050
Their family just had a third kid.

884
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,090
How do they have so many?

885
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,820
But those little ones were pretty sweet.

886
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:04,300
They kept calling me "Uncle" non-stop,

887
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:06,090
even recited "Memorial to Zhuge Liang" to me.

888
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:10,940
Hey, don't find me annoying, but

889
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,820
the medical checkup results are out.

890
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:15,010
Your thyroid hormone levels are still a bit high,

891
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:17,210
so you really need to keep adjusting.

892
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:20,820
Otherwise, all the effort from the past few months

893
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,090
will go to waste again.

894
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,490
Am I not trying hard enough already?

895
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,010
I even quit smoking.

896
00:36:27,030 --> 00:36:28,690
I've done everything you asked.

897
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:30,050
Don't put more pressure on me, okay?

898
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:30,980
Alright, no pressure.

899
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,650
Leave all these worries,

900
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:34,090
especially work-related ones,

901
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:35,940
to me, okay?

902
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,010
If anyone's gonna be stressed, let it be me.

903
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,380
- Alright. - Let it all come at me.

904
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:40,980
The water's boiling, go make your instant noodles.

905
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,820
I'll go make the noodles.

906
00:37:30,510 --> 00:37:31,460
Answer the phone.

907
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:53,420
Who is it?

908
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,170
Nutcase.

909
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:09,780
Looking even more handsome, Mr. Ji.

910
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:11,980
Did you read the materials I sent you?

911
00:38:13,590 --> 00:38:14,460
I'm talking to you!

912
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,980
You definitely agree with my plan, right?

913
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,490
Otherwise, you wouldn't have called me

914
00:38:18,510 --> 00:38:19,610
to the consultation.

915
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,420
Your plan is only theoretically feasible.

916
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:24,420
What about bleeding issues and postoperative complications?

917
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:25,460
Have you considered those?

918
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:28,010
Using an ultrasonic bone scalpel for simultaneous cutting and coagulation

919
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:29,860
can keep blood loss under 2,000 milliliters.

920
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:31,130
A total resection is doable.

921
00:38:32,230 --> 00:38:33,010
Did you even read it?

922
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:34,420
I'm asking you a question!

923
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:37,260
You called me at three in the morning,

924
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:39,170
and what time is it now?

925
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:39,940
Seven o'clock.

926
00:38:39,960 --> 00:38:41,260
There's still half an hour before the morning meeting.

927
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:42,860
Come on, let's go see Ms. Li.

928
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,090
You'll be the primary surgeon for this operation.

929
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,130
Go ahead and explain.

930
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,130
This paper shared by Qiao Yang

931
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:57,820
is a recent article from Liuyedao.

932
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:58,650
They also published

933
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:00,010
detailed video materials.

934
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:00,780
I've watched them,

935
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,010
and they are indeed quite insightful.

936
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:07,420
However, performing simultaneous cutting and coagulation

937
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:09,340
requires extensive clinical experience.

938
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,690
We've only done a few cases so far.

939
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:13,130
You just mentioned controlling blood loss to 2,000 milliliters,

940
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,490
we all know that's impossible.

941
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:16,010
Fang Ting's surgery itself

942
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:17,460
is extremely risky,

943
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,130
so I do not recommend

944
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,490
using such a risky surgical technique.

945
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,980
That's not what you said when you called me in

946
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,300
for the consultation.

947
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,010
I just asked you to listen in.

948
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:27,460
I never said I agreed with your plan.

949
00:39:29,030 --> 00:39:29,740
Ms. Li,

950
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:31,210
Fang Ting has talked to me many times

951
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:33,010
about wanting a total resection.

952
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:35,090
At both major and minor meetings,

953
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:36,740
haven't you always emphasized

954
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,650
that we should

955
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:39,420
respect the patient's wishes as much as possible?

956
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:42,490
Of course, we should respect their wishes,

957
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:45,130
but it has to be their genuine wishes.

958
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,010
Qiao,

959
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:49,420
surgery is meant to relieve the patient's suffering,

960
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:51,740
not to satisfy a doctor's desire for practice.

961
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,860
No, wait, you're confusing me.

962
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:58,010
Total resection is exactly what the patient truly wants.

963
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,900
Fang Ting told me herself.

964
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:01,740
She absolutely won't accept the plan

965
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,690
for a 20% partial resection...

966
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:03,490
Take a look at this.

967
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,010
The surgery plan has been finalized.

968
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,780
The primary surgeon will be the director.

969
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,860
Their skills are definitely not an issue.

970
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:21,780
By the way,

971
00:40:22,150 --> 00:40:23,940
about that red envelope...

972
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,900
Could you lend me a little more?

973
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:29,260
Don't worry.

974
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,340
I have something to deal with right now,

975
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,210
so I'll talk to you later.

976
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:35,300
Why did you sign the surgery consent form?

977
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,490
I've already thought of a new plan.

978
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:45,170
I'm still fighting for a total resection.

979
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:48,300
I don't wanna hear any more about it.

980
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:50,210
Why did you give up so quickly?

981
00:40:50,510 --> 00:40:51,610
You know that if you don't do it this time,

982
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:53,170
there will be even fewer chances in the future.

983
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,490
You were the one who told me

984
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:04,010
you didn't want to live like this anymore.

985
00:41:04,190 --> 00:41:04,940
I said fine,

986
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,900
we'll fight for it together.

987
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,530
I'm still gritting my teeth and holding on.

988
00:41:08,550 --> 00:41:10,490
You can't just pull the ladder out from under me and run away!

989
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:18,090
I know what you want.

990
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:20,740
Trust me,

991
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:22,210
okay?

992
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:25,650
I've been to hospitals all over the country.

993
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,780
Other than you,

994
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:29,210
no one else has promised me a total resection.

995
00:41:29,550 --> 00:41:32,420
Everyone gets scared just looking at such a huge tumor.

996
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:33,650
Only you,

997
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,610
you were so thrilled.

998
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:39,490
Telling me to take a gamble,

999
00:41:40,190 --> 00:41:41,740
like I'm your little lab rat.

1000
00:41:42,630 --> 00:41:43,860
If the surgery succeeds,

1001
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,380
you'll be famous.

1002
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,170
If it fails,

1003
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,010
I'm the one who dies.
